Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子 翔子！
